description.en:
[Promotional Manhwa]

I now possess the body of Ophelia, the villainess in the story 'The Crown Prince Returns'.
And just like the protagonists in the other reincarnated novels, I thought I would fare well.

I died by getting guillotined the first time, the second time was getting my limbs torn apart, third was suicide by poison, and by the fourth time, I was struck with arrows atop the throne.

And by the fifth restart, even if I tried to stray from the original storyline, I would still be doomed to die.

&quot;Concoct a poison for me. Not one that&rsquo;s painful, but one that&rsquo;ll kill me slowly.&quot;

Therefore, this time, with all my heart and soul, I wished to die properly for once.

&quot;After I ascend the throne, are you leaving me behind?&quot;
&quot;I sincerely hope that her highness survives, no matter what.&quot;
&quot;Your Highness, I wish to get to know you better.&quot;

All these people surrounding aren't letting me die off easily!
[hr][b][u]PT:[/u][/b]
[spoiler] Eu agora possuo o corpo de Ophelia, a vil&atilde; do romance &quot;O Pr&iacute;ncipe Retornou&quot;.
Assim como os outros protagonistas de romances sobre reencarna&ccedil;&atilde;o, achei que me sairia bem.

Mas n&atilde;o foi assim. Minha primeira execu&ccedil;&atilde;o foi com uma guilhotina, a segunda decapita&ccedil;&atilde;o, a terceira foi veneno e a quarta por uma flecha. 

Na quinta vez que retornei, mesmo tentando desviar do enredo original, estava condenada &agrave; morte.

&quot;Prepare um veneno para mim. Que me mate lentamente e sem dor.&quot;

Portanto, desta vez, com todo meu cora&ccedil;&atilde;o e alma, eu desejei morrer confortavelmente.

&quot;Depois que eu subir ao trono, voc&ecirc; vai me deixar para tr&aacute;s?&quot;
&quot;Eu sinceramente espero que Vossa Alteza sobreviva de alguma maneira.&quot;
&quot;Desejo conhec&ecirc;-la melhor, Alteza.&quot;

TODAS AS PESSOAS AO MEU REDOR N&Atilde;O ME DEIXAM MORRER FACILMENTE![/spoiler]
[hr][b][u]Russian / Русский:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]Я переродилась в романе &quot;Возвращение принца&quot;, и думала, что смогу прожить долгую и счастливую жизнь, как другие героини романов, но...

Я уже успела умреть 4 раза! После пятого перерождения, я поняла, что как бы я не меняла и как бы не следовала сюжету, итог один - смерть!

Поэтому, на этот раз, я хочу умереть спокойно и безболезненно...[/spoiler]
